## Etymology

*Rekha* (‡§∞‡•á‡§ñ‡§æ) is a Sanskrit/Hindi word meaning "line", "stroke", or "diagram". It seemed fitting for a library focused on creating beautiful line plots, scatter plots, and other visualizations.
